title: Episode 168: The Wish List (Feat. Lil Durk & Richelle Ryan)
itunes:title: Episode 168: The Wish List (Feat. Lil Durk & Richelle Ryan)
description:
Rapper Lil Durk and Pornstar Richelle Ryan join the ladies of Lip Service this week! Lil Durk opens up about his girlfriend India, what is off limits in the bedroom, and much more! Richelle Ryan and the crew speak about the ins and outs of the porn industry, how realistic it is, why she joined the industry, and things she'll never do on camera. Enjoy!
